skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Better Decisions is here to help you with tips and ideas that you can use in your everyday life. We all need help to make "better decisions", so we wanted to bring you ideas, tips, hacks, and thoughts about ways to do so. This is a flash briefing you'll want to hear every week that will actually help you make the most out of life that week using the tips that we give.

Enable the "Better Decisions" skill right now to be on your way to making better decisions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
